For those cooking for just 2 - here's a tip. Make the sauce as directed. Use just half of the sauce for two filets. Freeze the other half of the sauce. Next time you make it, just thaw your sauce in the microwave and proceed with the fish, breadcrumb topping and wine. I do this quite alot with various sauces and it's a real time/money saver when just cooking for two.

